W-What do you want me to do?

336
00:18:47,750 --> 00:18:49,310
Apart from Twelve Music House,

337
00:18:49,310 --> 00:18:50,030
I also raided

338
00:18:50,030 --> 00:18:51,630
all Jinwu Guards' barracks.

339
