He and Nan Jifeng were once

449
00:24:25,510 --> 00:24:26,950
military comrades.

450
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:30,030
Nan Jifeng's fled the country.

451
00:24:30,350 --> 00:24:32,060
Who knows if he has

452
00:24:32,510 --> 00:24:33,390
defected?

