558
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:16,980
About this matter,

559
00:29:18,270 --> 00:29:19,800
you mustn't tell the truth.

560
00:29:20,670 --> 00:29:21,270
But we can't

561
00:29:21,270 --> 00:29:22,530
